name: DEN_Octokuro
description:
Revised post of the model, due to my error in uploading.

Would love to see the creations people make from this.

An attempt at a textual inversion of my favourite looks. I wont have done a good job of these but get reasonable results with zovya and clarity2.

big thank you to Alyila for the guide.
